<plot>When Jeff Leland dies an untimely death, he leaves behind a father who, ashamed of the senseless loss, embarks on a road trip to get rid of a painful reminder. Unfortunately, he's stuck with another reminder; his grandson, Little Jack. Now the two must find a way to get along as each grieves in his own way.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?409409</url></doc>
